description: Delete an Amazon CloudFront VPC origin.

parameters.name: IfMatch
parameters.description: The version identifier of the VPC origin to delete. This is the ETag value returned in the response to  GetVpcOrigin.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The VPC origin last modified time.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_items.name: HTTPPort
nested_items.description: The HTTP port for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 80.

nested_items.name: HTTPSPort
nested_items.description: The HTTPS port of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 443.

nested_items.name: OriginProtocolPolicy
nested_items.description: The origin protocol policy for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_items.name: OriginSslProtocols
nested_items.description: A complex type that contains information about the SSL/TLS protocols that CloudFront can use when establishing an HTTPS connection with your origin.

nested_items.name: Quantity
nested_items.description: The number of SSL/TLS protocols that you want to allow CloudFront to use when establishing an HTTPS connection with this origin.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: A list that contains allowed SSL/TLS protocols for this distribution.
